hwMeta.bodyText:
If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        stash_origin_op(ORIGIN_TYPE.DELETE),
        lookup_in_progress(0),
        insertFsm(insertFsm_t.idle),
        cleanupAddr(0)
    ).Else(
        stash_origin_op(stash_origin_op_next),
        lookup_in_progress(lookup_in_progress_next),
        insertFsm(insertFsm_next),
        cleanupAddr(cleanupAddr_next)
    )
)

If(insertFsm._eq(insertFsm_t.idle),
    If(lookup_not_in_progress & clean_vld._eq(1),
        stash_origin_op_next(ORIGIN_TYPE.DELETE),
        stash_item_vld_next(0),
        stash_key_next(stash_key),
        stash_data_next(stash_data),
        stash_reinsert_cntr_next(stash_reinsert_cntr)
    ).Elif(lookup_not_in_progress & delete_vld._eq(1),
        stash_origin_op_next(ORIGIN_TYPE.DELETE),
        stash_key_next(delete_key),
        stash_item_vld_next(0),
        stash_data_next(stash_data),
        stash_reinsert_cntr_next(stash_reinsert_cntr)
    ).Elif(lookup_not_in_progress & insert_vld._eq(1),
        stash_origin_op_next(ORIGIN_TYPE.INSERT),
        stash_key_next(insert_key),
        stash_data_next(insert_data),
        stash_reinsert_cntr_next(15),
        stash_item_vld_next(1)
    ).Elif((lookup_vld & lookup_rd)._eq(1),
        stash_origin_op_next(ORIGIN_TYPE.LOOKUP),
        stash_key_next(lookup_key),
        stash_item_vld_next(stash_item_vld),
        stash_data_next(stash_data),
        stash_reinsert_cntr_next(stash_reinsert_cntr)
    ).Elif((tables_0_lookup_rd & tables_1_lookup_rd)._eq(1),
        stash_origin_op_next(ORIGIN_TYPE.DELETE),
        stash_key_next(None),
        stash_item_vld_next(stash_item_vld),
        stash_data_next(stash_data),
        stash_reinsert_cntr_next(stash_reinsert_cntr)
    ).Else(
        stash_origin_op_next(stash_origin_op),
        stash_item_vld_next(stash_item_vld),
        stash_key_next(stash_key),
        stash_data_next(stash_data),
        stash_reinsert_cntr_next(stash_reinsert_cntr)
    )
).Elif(lookupResNext,
    If(sig_2._eq(1),
        stash_key_next(tables_0_lookupRes_key),
        stash_data_next(tables_0_lookupRes_data),
        stash_reinsert_cntr_next((stash_reinsert_cntr._reinterpret_cast(Bits(4, signed=False)) - 1)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(4))),
        stash_item_vld_next(tables_0_lookupRes_occupied),
        stash_origin_op_next(stash_origin_op)
    ).Elif(sig_3._eq(1),
        stash_key_next(tables_1_lookupRes_key),
        stash_data_next(tables_1_lookupRes_data),
        stash_reinsert_cntr_next((stash_reinsert_cntr._reinterpret_cast(Bits(4, signed=False)) - 1)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(4))),
        stash_item_vld_next(tables_1_lookupRes_occupied),
        stash_origin_op_next(stash_origin_op)
    ).Else(
        stash_origin_op_next(ORIGIN_TYPE.DELETE),
        stash_key_next(None),
        stash_data_next(None),
        stash_reinsert_cntr_next(None),
        stash_item_vld_next(None)
    )
).Else(
    stash_origin_op_next(stash_origin_op),
    stash_item_vld_next(stash_item_vld),
    stash_key_next(stash_key),
    stash_data_next(stash_data),
    stash_reinsert_cntr_next(stash_reinsert_cntr)
)

If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    stash_reinsert_cntr(stash_reinsert_cntr_next),
    stash_key(stash_key_next),
    stash_item_vld(stash_item_vld_next),
    stash_data(stash_data_next),
    insertTargetOH(insertTargetOH_next),
    insertFinal(insertFinal_next)
)

hwMeta.name: insertFsm._eq(insertFsm_t.lookup) & stash_origin_op._eq(ORIGIN_TYPE.INSERT) & stash_reinsert_cntr._eq(0) | insertFsm._eq(insertFsm_t.lookupResAck) & (tables_0_insert_rd & tables_1_insert_rd)._eq(1) & insertFinal._eq(1) & ~(stash_origin_op._eq(ORIGIN_TYPE.DELETE))
